project_descr: Muthana Governorate Capacity Building and Institution Reinforcement Programme

outputs.output_descr:
Enhance the institutional and human resources capacities to provide efficiently social and basic services to the people of Muthanna.
1. Improve the capacity of local authorities and technical departments across Muthanna Governorate.
2. Improve the capacity of Muthanna Civil Defence.
3. Improve the capacity of the Agriculture institutions in Muthanna
Capacity Building and Institutional reinforcement of different Directorates in Muthanna Governorate

project_title: muthanna governorate capacity building and institution
